  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7256281d-e912-493a-bd63-ef046df52abf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03fd9cb5-782f-4ceb-af8c-e52d0bcca9bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e4a94ed5-586a-4097-9b39-ea443e3777c4\">안녕하세요. 연일 날씨가 춥습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-10089f70-176b-4f3d-9742-cc4553daeee9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-952cb267-e625-43a5-adc0-c454a39c1ac1\">이렇게 날씨가 추우면 아픈게 심해지죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-16387e41-13d5-40e6-88c9-51f5193f65c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-542485f7-3ca3-417b-96d3-1164e0f11642\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4eb71ba2-28b4-464e-a7ef-b339f1d46379\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8af38d7d-ed24-4078-a42d-162648390541\">특히 무릎 통증은 날씨가 추워지면 더 심해지게 마련입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b637eaf-f5fd-4d09-87d7-20ee063aca89\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e2786379-df8b-4b5b-a06d-cf5271668899\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2bd397c-cb12-401b-8f28-f5b04d707d50\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97519069-9034-4e85-b69d-e1bb40bcc12b\">이수한의원에 내원하시는 환자분들도 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1d08be5a-6257-4831-8d5c-a9b11f96a05d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5eb0a9ce-f26d-4ad8-8118-6589256555b5\">&#x27;치료받고 좋았는데 날씨가 추워서 그런가 또 아픈 것 같아&#x27; 라는 말을 하시는 분들이 종종 있네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-794269c0-c497-4839-a950-261b4b3b5aab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-10c95901-e137-4ff4-9644-b5f838cdc941\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-418b4f12-5c08-4505-86af-073dc879a544\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dede9d68-0a8e-40df-bc03-4b3ed782a4c2\">무릎이 아프면 무조건 관절염만 떠올리는 분들이 많으실텐데요, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4c8b8d59-9ec3-442b-8d2a-ddca8ba196c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-288739d2-aed1-417c-9309-0fd0f73677d8\">남성역 이수한의원에서 무릎이 아픈 여러가지 원인들을 알려드리겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b07496f9-a1a7-4459-b1dc-2bcd58bf897f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-35451d5f-ba8f-4b48-a5bc-6fa270111315\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0940051-84ee-46b4-96af-2942fd48f7e3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f0940051-84ee-46b4-96af-2942fd48f7e3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f1c9ce51068b46e5.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f1c9ce51068b46e5.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f1c9ce51068b46e5.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-66d35848-1435-4e5f-bdca-00de6069e99d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-66d35848-1435-4e5f-bdca-00de6069e99d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a4bb0e21f8c5807.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a4bb0e21f8c5807.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4a4bb0e21f8c5807.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a023086-e79d-4b25-a910-9a75e27e65c7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-17249e5a-60f9-4b29-8aab-ff795cfb7c8a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-303036aa-8220-4d5f-9c75-a801bb1aef1c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f0ed6c06-c95f-4078-9273-a272ada9fd33\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-35e0cd22-e418-4425-bb35-5c59b714e7e1\">근육 또는 근막 통증으로 인해 무릎이 아픈 경우는 너무 많죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b59aca08-efa0-46dd-8144-caeea11890e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f5193987-2e6c-488d-92c7-c4f2af642de8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-923d8d0f-9643-4509-88e0-7ec16ce4a67d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-923d8d0f-9643-4509-88e0-7ec16ce4a67d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ee96e3c982a7d6.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ee96e3c982a7d6.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ee96e3c982a7d6.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5ac463d6-70d4-4bbc-af49-4f3f06b78b92\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e9c6f27-1acc-4a68-89f0-61d02c36d51c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5dd3ebcd-ae47-4d16-aa0e-0521335f6403\">최근에 20대 초반 여자 환자분이 무릎이 아프다고 남성역 이수한의원으로 내원했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1d1847fe-dd22-4508-856a-a8f48cf2ad25\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2eab9d9c-2dcd-4b06-b8ea-1a35e800a285\">벌써 몇년째 아프다고 하더군요. 이 젊은 분이 퇴행성 무릎 관절염이 있지는 않을텐데 왜 아팠을까요. 이런저런 문진과 진찰, 검사를 진행했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f2a48b4-16a9-40da-b7e3-4772dafc631d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4a823b7f-6fef-416b-99ef-5b88901eeca5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6220f8d2-c891-4924-b006-643cc06c1f39\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1899d296-83c1-4ad3-8aaf-39af1c64c46a\">어떨때 아픈가요? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9c1db942-af57-4ea7-b88a-14d0fb4c3826\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5db0f4e2-0681-406e-b5f6-1567f02afe52\">무릎 꿇어 앉으면 바닥에 닿는 부위가 너무 아파요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d262186d-0141-4a64-a974-a43fa6eaaf33\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3c6b83de-5b27-4d54-940c-c4b2741b9fc5\">그래서 꿇어앉을때 바닥에 닿는 부위를 만져봤습니다. 살짝만 눌러도 많이 아파하네요. 그 뿐아니고 슬개건 부위 전체적으로 다 만지면 아팠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c17bde55-a81f-40d9-b7dd-7d07df7218cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdf720c9-88b1-40eb-a441-de7588240021\">운동을 열심히 한 후 아파진 건 아닌데 왜 슬개건이 아플까. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1be7b500-6252-4a62-88e1-68334ae5b42f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-682b73ac-3e3c-4ca6-a667-05b26a74eec4\">슬개건에 연결된 허벅지 근육을 검사해보니 허벅지 근육이 너무 약합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e74ccd9e-a99d-4537-8748-990c6eec3fe2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8eb3fad4-1566-4340-9906-69693217e652\">최근에 헬스를 시작했다 하는데, 스쿼트 같은 하체 근력운동을 할 때 괜찮은지 물어보니 그런 동작을 할때 아프다고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-32b50e93-7f7a-4f82-b9a7-c0973cea3420\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-49ec1345-9ea8-415e-a804-c1c68f6cbd01\">왼쪽 발목의 &#x27;거골&#x27;이라는 뼈를 만져보니 아프다고 합니다. 어려서 발목을 다쳤던 적이 있다고 하구요. 발목을 다쳤어도 몇 년 지나면 상처는 다 아물게 마련인데, 아직도 통증이 남아있어요. 척추의 앞쪽 근육도 약하고, 엉덩이 근육도 약합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2081d43d-ce30-4c22-987f-9ea2c996ed89\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2479ba60-8a0f-481e-a737-1cac3996bff3\">허리 아프지 않냐 물으니, 허리도 너무 아픈데 무릎이 더 심해서 허리아프다는 말은 안했다고 하네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4254d5f0-76f6-48f9-8b3b-e9845cdf18ae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a48cfdb-03a1-43d2-9bbb-c2d4384921a9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b66f7c74-1643-45e2-abb1-d8cf61a8d1f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6052ba47-b509-4fd0-8629-cbb49bcec311\">슬개건염으로 진단을 하고 약침치료와 침치료를 시술했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-239992de-5140-443a-98d9-e1a45b77e306\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d8198d45-05fe-4116-b637-375ff50c27f8\">슬개건염이 낫지 않고 계속 재발되고 지속되는 이유는 발목과 무릎 주변 근육의 약화 때문이라 판단하고 추나요법을 통해 근육을 강화하고 틀어진 척추, 골반을 교정했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d93574b6-33bf-4f25-926f-732ddb5c8e11\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-61b639d6-0417-49f9-868f-b61b08e310da\">추나 치료 후 바로 근력이 좋아짐을 확인하고 본인도 깜짝 놀란 표정입니다 ^^</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c55016c0-dcd6-400c-b6b1-10d441edbfd3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fdf05180-46ce-4048-87a3-bc8ac473d332\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-89a8a093-ab7f-44a9-ac01-5d5550c1aea9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7617f25e-8f29-4157-ac0a-f2866ed68698\">치료를 지속하면 수년간 이어져온 무릎 통증이 치료될 수 있을거라 기대됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e120a6a-58d4-4dea-933a-957d7344f8a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-421e43a0-25a7-4801-923a-8d2421ad6bdc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fdd4bc08-f002-44d5-91c2-d988c845dc1e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fdd4bc08-f002-44d5-91c2-d988c845dc1e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b887b758b54607b4.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b887b758b54607b4.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b887b758b54607b4.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2862e969-582f-4449-bc16-0dd05473a0f5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20bb4f23-89fa-4331-9fc4-d38897113df6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc614d0d-bf44-4532-89cb-bc5bc972210c\">다치지 않았는데 무릎 안쪽이 아프다는 경우, 거위발건염일 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-976ecd4f-99ba-43d2-86ed-27d94b65bd48\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2e1fa010-2b22-439d-9839-15509b0fb60d\">예전에 건물 관리를 하시는 분이 무릎 안쪽이 아프다면서 내원했었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-37ab70ae-31c7-4570-9e32-19bb6a45eca5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3636f776-42ee-44c7-b5f4-b41c0a024f71\">진찰 후 거위발건염을 설명드리고 치료를 해드렸었죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9897bcb-89cf-49da-be46-212ff29305c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1f9594c7-2648-4c86-b1af-26aaea61736d\">다음날 출근했더니 그 분이 대기실에서 고래고래 소리를 지르면서 원장을 찾는겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-acb370c4-6f39-46ad-8a84-b9fcac8b62f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e6d33425-078c-487e-a8d2-9b49ee005b7b\">무슨일인가했더니..</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6564830e-1e38-45f9-827c-d11d7206b91e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-93007c87-e02a-4afc-a3fe-ee3c8cc7d8c2\">어제 한 번 치료 받고 무릎이 싹 다 나아서 고맙다는 인사 하고 싶다고 저를 찾았답니다. ㅎㅎ  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c14e64bc-be54-4b69-a7a3-08e82f8fbc50\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dbda328c-df42-40a3-8df4-83245a8af665\">정말, 성격 화끈한 분이셨습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b73c723d-10a4-4bfd-a3f5-653d14d6ea2b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b73c723d-10a4-4bfd-a3f5-653d14d6ea2b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16faf65ae7d141ea.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16faf65ae7d141ea.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/16faf65ae7d141ea.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-90336857-0e41-4865-9d93-1059ee5a98a5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e426ed0f-5a28-4b44-89e5-de62da696602\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-54cf73fe-3e54-43e6-9fba-99db8e103bd5\">등산하는분, 트레킹 하는 분, 간혹 축구나 마라톤 하는 분들이 무릎 외측 통증을 호소할때 꼭 확인해봐야 합니다. 보통, 무리한 운동 후에 잘 생기죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-876a7cc0-6017-4bb7-b702-be0b1d52d348\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-876a7cc0-6017-4bb7-b702-be0b1d52d348\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d45841c58b1eb0c.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d45841c58b1eb0c.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d45841c58b1eb0c.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81c5acec-26b8-4cb1-961e-5e572707647f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e3fffc8-a612-4192-b7ed-42c21a624da0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-579ea105-a1eb-4a52-9914-b6f6ae331025\">인대파열이니 환자 본인이 왜 아프게 됐는지, 어떻게 다쳤는지를 명확하게 알고 있는 경우가 대부분입니다. 많은 경우 운동손상이고, 계단 눈길 등에서 미끄러져서 발생하는 경우도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eeedebdd-808e-4176-a944-90507808980b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-22b420d0-b909-4123-b40d-d24dedb12795\">십자인대, 내측측부인대, 외측측부인대.. 등 손상 당시의 상황에 따라 파열되는 인대가 달라집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c52057fc-c7df-4871-9122-27151df0a995\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c52057fc-c7df-4871-9122-27151df0a995\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79b310d648eedc56.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79b310d648eedc56.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79b310d648eedc56.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9063e050-748d-4540-8338-e1a9601ffc53\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-93e3b715-225d-433c-af35-18840e3c39a2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-227f234a-27b7-4187-852f-3726d6849e91\">젊은 분들은 부상에 의해 발생하지만, 나이들면 퇴행으로 인해 생길 수도 있습니다. 한국인의 자세습관(바닥에 책상다리 등) 때문인지 한국인은 반월판 문제가 더 빈번하다고 합니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6ce3de7c-2c17-4ce8-b9de-e512f71422aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c719d107-56c4-470e-b28c-0a0f5e779d17\">반월판 손상이 의심되면 MRI 촬영 후 관절경 수술을 진행하곤 하는데, 수술없이도 치료할 수 있으니 이수한의원에서 비수술치료를 먼저 받아보길 권합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-adb47ccf-997f-4080-81d8-674d96786eb2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39b5421c-1615-44a3-a5f7-f51d90804850\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d530f243-59a1-4fba-a465-ebd73a220093\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8caf0c5a-4ea0-4a5c-910f-15c36ae7b217\"><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222947563402\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222947563402</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-0374c07e-05b3-4cce-b4d5-0f3f96c595b1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222947563402\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogthumb.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMjEyMDZfNjUg%2FMDAxNjcwMzAwNjc2NTg1.5Omy9anHQTSoOuNQOHAlzbDfXR-x1k47C_1j7dqV3Xwg.hfhpCI-7rraBfyy5yg5bA7h0V1mGNrXpwipwRdQQtPsg.PNG.isuhani%2F%25B4%25D9%25BE%25E7%25C7%25D1_%25B9%25DD%25BF%25F9%25C6%25C7_%25BC%25D5%25BB%25F3%25C0%25C7_%25BE%25E7%25BB%25F3.png%3Ftype%3Dw2%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222947563402\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">반월판(반월상 연골) 손상 진단으로 관절경 수술을 받은 환자 이야기</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">안녕하세요. 동작구, 7호선 남성역 앞 이수한의원 입니다. 오늘 반월판(반월상연골)에 대한 자료를 보다가 ...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">blog.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-0374c07e-05b3-4cce-b4d5-0f3f96c595b1\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/222947563402\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogthumb.pstatic.net%2FMjAyMjEyMDZfNjUg%2FMDAxNjcwMzAwNjc2NTg1.5Omy9anHQTSoOuNQOHAlzbDfXR-x1k47C_1j7dqV3Xwg.hfhpCI-7rraBfyy5yg5bA7h0V1mGNrXpwipwRdQQtPsg.PNG.isuhani%2F%25B4%25D9%25BE%25E7%25C7%25D1_%25B9%25DD%25BF%25F9%25C6%25C7_%25BC%25D5%25BB%25F3%25C0%25C7_%25BE%25E7%25BB%25F3.png%3Ftype%3Dw2%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fa67bb83-7392-423a-b719-bc21dd91415b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fa67bb83-7392-423a-b719-bc21dd91415b\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/771615a0f605be1c.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/771615a0f605be1c.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/771615a0f605be1c.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f462b36-774f-4afc-9198-1d12b005a2f0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-47a2a1aa-9170-4fe2-b896-cdfd2c27e9ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b7fce7ff-7f8e-4fea-b381-c69038b2c97b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9890eac0-8ba2-4ebf-baad-bc7a0e3a34eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4af81699-eca0-4aab-a99f-14c70ea2b719\">여러 다양한 원인들이 있다고는 하지만, 결국 나이가 들면 퇴행성관절염이 발생하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e1458ced-fb8a-49c5-be82-59961c4b3ee1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0ab5a608-95c2-4033-87b8-d16d901c90b5\">다만 퇴행성관절염 진단을 받더라도, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef08fa53-9e19-4cc0-9853-38da246b2f7c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a0e9c9c4-0587-41d0-92b3-51ff726c1485\">1. 퇴행성 관절염 단독으로 통증의 원인이 되는 경우와 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a1be19f-61d0-4791-be85-d6d04c29c3d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cae0e1ee-cd9c-4c0b-a65e-7479d1952579\">2.다른 질환(근육, 힘줄, 인대, 반월판 등)이 함께 통증의 원인이 되는 경우를 구별해야 하겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-590351d8-8b83-4d3a-8ca2-0c7adb39e927\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f21c8e9e-18a0-428f-b160-283c35914553\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2722a423-95c2-47c4-bcb3-f60b9004730b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-54af1539-7574-4cd6-a3ea-f50486da850a\">다른 원인이 함께 있는 경우에는 퇴행성관절염 외의 다른 원인을 먼저 치료했을때, 퇴행성관절염이 그대로 있더라도 무릎 통증은 사라질 수 있거든요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-200c7717-f2a9-4ad3-a80a-27b2dc439c4d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b5cc17f2-8112-406c-8719-eb0800393c53\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-79deb6af-cf7e-4f16-9c0e-37cea4741b6b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-176e9870-bb2d-467e-ad00-f4cf5d63ad7e\">이수한의원에서는 다른원인질환과 퇴행성관절염을 동시에 고려해서 치료를 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5eadce42-cf4e-4f10-b5d0-7ded883e6541\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ad4980b6-357f-4d86-a2f6-bacc1f9416d6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-04e5750f-b62c-4c0d-ac84-966ac21bb20d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0caadcb-2f75-49e6-83bc-7f9914f3938d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e6080bfb-ad69-4091-99b7-5c50e8824927\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2d64111a-a0be-48eb-a472-04515d0126b2\">무릎이 아플때, 그 원인을 잘 파악해서 치료하면 소염진통제의 오남용을 줄이고, 시술 및 수술을 피할 수 있을 겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b453d025-a5e3-402e-9a38-21029bbecf24\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2412717d-9212-4b5a-91cf-91b40849f42c\">또한 무릎이 아플때는 무릎관절 뿐 아니라 그 위아래에 있는 골반, 고관절과 발목관절의 문제가 있는지도 확인을 해야 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f0f3437e-a554-4ee0-b5ec-25bf75a6b661\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fdcfa1bd-0016-4f19-9ef7-3edd32abc07f\">발목이 약하면 무릎관절에 계속 부담을 주게되어 무릎 통증이 잘 치료되지 않습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ed86b8da-5115-4b66-9f11-dd9ccebff81e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d480b21a-327f-43e8-8ed0-94dc55293fbb\">골반 고관절이 굳어있거나 약해져 있어도 무릎관절에 부담이 증가하여 치료를 방해하고 무릎 통증이 자꾸 재발되게 만드는 원인이 되니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d52d55e1-80a1-4737-a7e8-a990e5f08e0b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b1b06c2e-7cd4-4e2a-a775-84d9e33eb084\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-908d8d94-c242-40b5-81ed-760d9dd40438\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c511befb-c4e4-4ee7-9642-93a653d74a31\">이수한의원에서는 한약, 약침, 침치료와 추나치료 등을 병행하여 무릎관절 뿐 아니라 연관된 다른 관절, 근육, 힘줄, 자세, 습관 등까지 치료하고 교정을 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97c16e69-354e-429d-9cc8-75c1a5315f01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7cb8fdc9-7991-431b-9ead-1738866b9b3f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bfcbc202-3ded-4135-8a8a-aacc3ea7f0ca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ad6a05a-7cde-4966-9214-770fb05a7e95\">이수한의원 의료진은 격주로 질환에 대한 연구와 임상노하우를 공유하는 스터디를 꾸준히 진행하고 있습니다. 더 나은 진단, 더 나은 치료를 위해 계속해서 노력하는 이수한의원이 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-291c27bc-8519-4d3b-805f-f815d13f9f1f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebbc3bfe-bf4b-4ca4-9e38-1996ee9db27a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ebd7c065-64fe-453a-a5f6-ba9ed59e5d56\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4fc8e029-a31f-4558-812e-8444ba95d110\"><a href=\"https://isumedical.modoo.at/\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://isumedical.modoo.at/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-image\" id=\"SE-e7e38d44-5026-4002-a2be-80c1960cdd22\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://isumedical.modoo.at/\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fmodo-phinf.pstatic.net%2F20221206_42%2F1670337066670KLF8b_PNG%2FmosaUSGN3u.png%3Ftype%3Df320_320%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"https://isumedical.modoo.at/\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">[이수한의원 - 홈] 끊임없는 연구를 통해 더 나은 치료를 약속드립니다</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">동작구 사당동 남성역 1번 출구 앞, 이수한의원입니다.</p>\n                  